==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Molotov cocktail
<hw>Molotov cocktail</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A home-made incendiary
device consisting of a bottle filled with gasoline, and a cloth wick.
The wick is lighted, and the bottle thrown at a target, such as a
vehicle, where it may shatter and spread intense flames over the
vehicle, destroying or damaging it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Molt</ent>⟦br⟧
